Elotu enkolong o Laitoriani


1  “Amu ng'ura; elotu enkolong napejisho anaa olmoti le nkima, ina pee eaku ilooitokoos o laasak pooki loo ng'ok isuut; ore ina olong nalotu napejoo ninche, ejo Olaitoriani loo lororani, melekaki ninch entonai anaa olng'osila. 
2  Kake ore iyie oure enkarna ai, keilepaki intae enkolong e supatisho eetae enkishiunoto too naipuko enyena. Ipuopuo intae intigiranana anaa ilasho ooti ooitigiran epuku to lale. 
3  Naa intunyokiki enkop iltorrok. Amu keaku nkuruon tiabori ndapi oo nkejek inyi ina olong naas ina Olaitoriani loo lororani.


4  “Entadamu inkiguanat o sinka lai Musa, o nkitanapat naitanapa ninye to ldoinyo le Horeb naaipirta Israel pooki.


5   “Ng'ura, kairriwaki nanu intae Eliya oloiboni le Nkai eton eitu elotu ina olong torrono o Laitoriani. 
6  Naa keibelekenyaki ninye iltauja loo menye inkera enye, neibelekenyaki sii iltauja loo nkera iloo menye, malotu ake aosh enkop to ldeket.”

